# Environment Variables — NutritionCoach

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values.
`.env` is gitignored and must never be committed.

```bash
# ── Required ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your free API key from https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_google_ai_studio_api_key_here

# ── Optional overrides (all have defaults in application.yml) ────────
# SERVER_PORT=8080
# Spring AI 1.0.0 uses the OpenAI-compatible endpoint of Google AI Studio:
#   base-url is pre-set to https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai
# SPRING_AI_OPENAI_CHAT_OPTIONS_MODEL=gemini-1.5-pro
```

## Quick start

```bash
export GEMINI_API_KEY=<your key>
./mvnw spring-boot:run
```

Then hit:
- `GET  http://localhost:8080/api/health`
- `POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat`         body: `{"message":"What are good sources of protein?"}`
- `POST http://localhost:8080/api/research-summary`  body: `{"topic":"omega-3 fatty acids"}`
- `GET  http://localhost:8080/h2-console`       (H2 browser console, dev only)
- `GET  http://localhost:8080/actuator/health`
